    <h4 class="centered blue-text">How it works</h4>
    <div class="centered">

      <div class="row large-padding-home ">
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3 pictures-resized"><%=image_tag("createprofileicon.png")%></div>
        <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"><h5 class="top-padding-text-limited">1. Create a profile</h5>
          Tell us about yourself — your skills, your
          preferred benefits, and your deal breakers.
        Our application respects your time.</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Since the items ordering on bootstrap doesn't work, hide the wrong content on xs to display the ordered one -->
      <div class="hidden-xs-down">
        <div class="row large-padding-home">
          <div class="col-sm-9 col-md-9"><h5>2. Search jobs</h5>
            Review job listings that match your unique
            self. Filter lists further or adjust preferences
          to see more or less jobs. </div>
          <div class="col-sm-3 col-md-3 pictures-resized"><%=image_tag("filtericon.png")%></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden-sm-up">
        <div class="row large-padding-home">
