            Review job listings that match your unique
            self. Filter lists further or adjust preferences
          to see more or less jobs. </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row large-padding-home flex-steps">
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3 pictures-resized"><%=image_tag("applicationicon.png")%></div>
        <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-9"><h5 class="top-padding-text-limited">3. Apply </h5>
          Apply for jobs and add a custom message to
          go with it. Your application will be reviewed
